{"tid":1437611,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"不患貧，患不均才是真相","createTime":"2019-08-09T14:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T19:05:42.000Z","uid":149978,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"18882ede73906a7e36954688945d9efee94eb6a1","tid":1437611,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:44:19.000Z","msg":"不患貧，患不均<br />\n證明左這個才是事實<br />\n中國走「先讓部分人富起來」隨時出事<br />\n<br />\n2003年，香港經濟差，回歸信心危機 + 金融風暴 + SARS恐慌 + 失業率8.7% + 基本法23條 + 董建華講野口疾疾 == 50萬人和平上街<br />\n<br />\n2019年，香港經濟算比較好，失業率低，但天價租金 + 天價樓價 + 物價貴 + 貧富懸殊 + 無良業主剝削 ，再配合逃犯條例修訂（送中條例） = 200萬人上街 + 暴力衝擊"},{"pid":"09e6e21de41704b394bb6e3c1ac40973f110ef9b","tid":1437611,"uid":51021,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:47:02.000Z","msg":"Joe gor出post 屌左你老母先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd7e3adbff4c4a102d0af0914a1843447f35b68","tid":1437611,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"09e6e21de41704b394bb6e3c1ac40973f110ef9b","tid":1437611,"uid":51021,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:47:02.000Z","msg":"Joe gor出post 屌左你老母先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:49:27.000Z","msg":"香港真係一個福地<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/818852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/818852</a><br />\n<br />\n點解搞成咁呀？"},{"pid":"56f1d1d980bafa7ce3c9e113f8d15a231404cf8a","tid":1437611,"uid":51021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:53:25.000Z","msg":"走啦on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00a7b96f0d82fafd8d64113db51fd1d6be752ec","tid":1437611,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"56f1d1d980bafa7ce3c9e113f8d15a231404cf8a","tid":1437611,"uid":51021,"like":1